      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "IZZY LETTS (4) has a terrific record this track and trip with four wins and two placings from six starts. In the money last time at Murray Bridge (22.44) in a Grade 5, finishing a 3.5 lengths second. Looks suited here and rates on top. ONE MARGARITA (2) hasn't been far away, finishing in the money twice in a row including last time in a Grade 6 at Murray Bridge over 300m. Speedy beginner who should be in the action early from an inside box. Can improve sharply here. TOORA TERRY (1) is having his first look at this course. Comes here a last start placegetter at Murray Bridge in a Grade 5 (22.74). Likely to be in the finish again. SECRET SUPER (7) has won at this course and distance – sure to figure prominently.",
